Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.10,0:01:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 這股奇怪的感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.99,0:01:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我隱約覺得這城市的氣氛有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.47,0:01:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在看這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.37,0:01:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我們進城開始 一直
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.39,0:01:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棺引人注目?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.12,0:01:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.49,0:02:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡 他們是在看你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.59,0:02:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你長相打扮是挺顯眼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.90,0:02:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可又不是從沒見過年輕女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.26,0:02:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.50,0:02:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡一個年輕女性都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.13,0:02:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是用於機杖的粉末化石思念料
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這點?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能賣給您的只有這麼多…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此地 化石思念料產地 產量維馬克王國第一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說 這伊貝克市
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.48,0:02:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是加瓦爾尼公爵領最大的化石思念料市場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持有現金
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.34,0:02:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.03,0:02:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我庫存不多 除去本地要用的數量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能賣給外來者的只有這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.70,0:03:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近收獲量減少了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.79,0:03:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這倒沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.98,0:03:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 最近領主大人徵收的數量驟增…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.52,0:03:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領主…加瓦爾尼公爵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他為什麼需要那麼多呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.89,0:03:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 總之這些就是所有的量了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說我在街上完全看不到年輕女性的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這有什麼特殊原因嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.65,0:03:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公爵大人每隔幾天就會派人帶走城裡少女回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.60,0:03:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派他的直屬軍隊來 半強制性地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強行帶走?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被帶走的女孩再沒有回來過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.36,0:03:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是生是死都還是未知數…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至還有人害怕得試圖逃出城市…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.14,0:03:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但聽說都被抓住 給殺掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.95,0:03:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我勸你們也盡快離開較好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不准什麼時候「少女狩獵」就又要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若在我這爭鬥起來 小店也承受不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.69,0:04:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡 付賬咱們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒人去宅邸探望一下女孩們的情況嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.70,0:04:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為公爵大人現在的宅邸…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.46,0:04:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.65,0:04:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航天要塞?

Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.66,0:04:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翱翔天際的要塞

Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是這裡領主的城堡?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.54,0:04:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航天要塞索厄拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是賈茲帝國首都攻防戰時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.81,0:04:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維馬克王國派出的兩座要塞之一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在因受到魔法攻擊而返回的途中 緊急迫降
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就順勢推給了加瓦爾尼領進行管理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.34,0:04:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而加瓦爾尼擅自進行了修理 乘上它到處飛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那領主到底在想些什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.02,0:05:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.37,0:05:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜集化石思念料
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.73,0:05:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來也是為了驅動那大得要命的要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.71,0:05:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且還掠走一大堆女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.69,0:05:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是有夠蹊蹺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.69,0:05:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 這也使那個傳聞增添了一份可信度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果加瓦爾尼公爵入手賈茲皇帝的遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.87,0:05:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的理由原本是個謎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.98,0:05:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但若是為了用作魔力源 驅動航天要塞…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實說得通
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.13,0:05:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之既然有傳聞說他持有遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就有必要進去確認下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.47,0:05:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.45,0:05:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能用魔法來飛上天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困難 專用機杖 需要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 只能再去拜託那傢伙了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你能飛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了 芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後你就願意和我打嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:06:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 要等從那成功回收了遺體之後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.18,0:06:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對 我們說定了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.08,0:06:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯 約定 重要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要與不死身裝鎧龍幹架呢 不能為我著想一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是不死身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被破壞了腦部還是會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前我先得掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.49,0:06:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要殺兄長請便 但我還要製成標本
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要留下太大傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.35,0:06:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自商量個什麼呢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾多妮卡 繼續靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.40,0:06:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺體 定在裡面 我確信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.28,0:06:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯 阿卡莉 突入突入
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我講過這次只是來探查
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.68,0:06:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調查清楚了再說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.57,0:06:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到合適的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.51,0:06:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.84,0:07:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要真能輕鬆被突入
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.74,0:07:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就說不上是什麼要塞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯 突入趕緊地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.35,0:07:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽不到剛才說進不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.76,0:07:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長 怎辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子這東西只能從內側打開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內側…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眾民傾聽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公爵宅聘請傭人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.06,0:07:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想為公爵效勞的人 立即站出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想為公爵效勞的人 站出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.37,0:07:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.16,0:07:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人是加瓦爾尼公爵家顧問魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛拉特·藍斯亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:07:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請先到別間等候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:08:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詳細指示稍候再予以通知
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是倉庫和空房間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令室在更上面?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.76,0:08:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 從構造上來講應該是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知公爵是否也在那兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然越往上戒備越森嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.13,0:08:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強行衝上去?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.99,0:08:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,著急不得啊 薇薇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.81,0:08:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們多花些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.90,0:08:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交份詳盡的報告書給基烈特大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我說的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.71,0:09:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當初使者被殺時 就該派兵強攻挫掉對方的銳氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.30,0:09:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再磨蹭下去 加瓦爾尼公爵都要攻到這卡德威爾來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.30,0:09:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前我的部下正在收集情報及確認情況
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.73,0:09:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在報告傳來之前還請再給一些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.67,0:09:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪還有這份閒空
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應盡快編制討伐部隊 以最大兵力進行討伐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 事已至此…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武力制裁也是迫不得已的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.49,0:09:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下 請下決斷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.47,0:09:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.79,0:09:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能如此了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命聯軍以航天要塞史特拉托斯為中心組成討伐軍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.61,0:09:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對加瓦爾尼公爵進行討伐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定期聯絡 關於航天要塞索厄拉的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.71,0:09:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要塞內部除偶有士兵巡邏外
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎沒有人的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.85,0:09:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出奇的安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:10:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加瓦爾尼公爵自我們潛入以來還從沒有現身過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具體統管要塞事務的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是自稱葛拉特·藍斯亞的魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾有一次見到名貴族打扮的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與葛拉特·藍斯亞在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是加瓦爾尼公爵的親屬?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.93,0:10:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與我們一起進來的女性們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被轉移到休息室後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被分成了幾波人 移動到了別處
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.19,0:10:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加瓦爾尼公爵的真意何在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又到底是為何驅動這航天要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將繼續調查
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.64,0:10:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇·荷羅派涅 芷依塔·布魯薩斯可
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,康拉德機關長傳來緊急通訊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基烈特隊長 事情不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的意思是…?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗登 隨同部隊準備如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.28,0:10:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先遣隊已出發前往加瓦爾尼領
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.68,0:11:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來只待閣下的號令了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全軍聽令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.65,0:11:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻起我航天要塞史特拉托斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及西方第六軍團 將出發討伐逆賊加瓦爾尼公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.83,0:11:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的要塞也正因喜悅而顫抖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.38,0:11:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出動史特拉托斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可 可這樣一來…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.24,0:11:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖有盡力勸阻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:11:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但未能推翻決定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.48,0:12:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討伐部隊將於明早抵達加瓦爾尼領
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即刻開始攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於你潛入索厄拉的兩名隊員
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.23,0:12:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還請你轉達消息 讓她們想辦法自行逃離
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.95,0:12:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了啊 小梟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願她們兩人能平安逃離啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 在那無處可逃的天上…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢地…小心點飛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.43,0:12:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯 慎重 重要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.30,0:12:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.19,0:12:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很準時
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠近過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.57,0:13:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上咯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.70,0:13:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯 問題無?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾多妮卡 侵入成功
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.07,0:13:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是武器庫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.09,0:13:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.27,0:13:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內部情形探查得怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一帶沒什麼有價值的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若有遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那應該在上面有司令室的階層
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要塞的支柱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,0:13:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能 機杖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:13:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機杖? 這麼大隻?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.68,0:14:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航天要塞 驅動 機杖 需要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔力 巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機杖 巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.97,0:14:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得要吃那麼多化石思念料了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.53,0:14:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這應該是升降機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.61,0:14:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘上這個能一口氣到上面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.81,0:14:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要坐這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.10,0:14:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可若到站就被圍住 那就成甕中之鱉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有其他路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.96,0:14:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.90,0:14:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿卡莉 分頭行動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.16,0:14:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還跑得動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:14:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯 芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.49,0:15:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 不過裝鎧龍自帶治癒能力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那點小傷死不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.86,0:15:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都明白目標是遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要往上走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.32,0:15:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總能在哪遇上芙蕾多妮卡和阿卡莉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是覺得剛才那幫士兵不太尋常
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.32,0:15:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋常 不是?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作出奇的整齊劃一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且受到攻擊別說痛叫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連吃痛的表現都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣? 能用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 雖然型號有些舊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知能否趁這騷亂 潛去上面調查
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白你想幫到基烈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.23,0:16:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要謹慎行事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.67,0:16:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.60,0:16:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次情況怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前兩人獨處時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.33,0:16:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣…我說了才沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定期聯絡的時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.85,0:16:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該還沒到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老鼠抓到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.89,0:16:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你鬧得挺歡的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.41,0:16:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到這最後關頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.91,0:16:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混進來了些有趣的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.70,0:16:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到入侵者了啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.31,0:16:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.69,0:16:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是里加爾圖·加瓦爾尼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加瓦爾尼公爵的孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.43,0:16:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我是最小的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是受聯合國指示闖進來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要這麼說 人數也太少了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.98,0:16:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說 只是探查情況的密探嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.77,0:16:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.23,0:17:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們派過來的使者 變成了什麼樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.05,0:17:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解體亂破師我還是第一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.36,0:17:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心臟 是什麼顏色的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.77,0:17:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個愛好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別喜歡切割人的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,細緻肢解得四分五裂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.87,0:17:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要問我理由 我也答不上來喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我生來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.24,0:17:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是惡趣味的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.91,0:17:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想看看你父母長啥樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.93,0:17:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你指加瓦爾尼公爵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你見不到他了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.27,0:17:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論父親還是母親 哥哥還是姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都已經分解掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.61,0:17:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里加爾圖大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這女孩身體素質很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.96,0:17:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥本領也很高
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.14,0:17:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得利用她追捕入侵者較為合適
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.95,0:17:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.06,0:17:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 現在是關鍵時刻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.09,0:17:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是主謀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.16,0:17:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以這麼說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.53,0:18:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但實際驅動這座要塞的是葛拉特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.55,0:18:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們三人 只是目的相同才一起行動而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.77,0:18:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要請你去幫忙抓捕同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.89,0:18:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 用力吸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若想用魔法控制人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必須侵入精神 時刻進行控制
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.93,0:18:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那遠遠不夠完美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.40,0:18:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能設置命令的中繼點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.82,0:18:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將人在保持人格的狀態下進行操縱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.28,0:18:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼即使控制整支軍隊也不在話下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.35,0:18:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ulu suei innu turun im contu naikt muei
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Luwai ulkait ennu ortz zuin kohku Nahl auyu atsuro sib tolug
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:19:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我完成的魔法術式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.35,0:19:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應感到榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.76,0:19:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯現吧 奪取服從者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.48,0:19:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿卡莉 令人擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.41,0:19:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 得盡快匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜得讓人不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過對我們是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.76,0:19:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.95,0:19:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想稍微到房間外看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.95,0:19:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.18,0:19:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被帶來的女孩之一嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.05,0:19:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城鎮的人 強制帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小偷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.67,0:19:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從外面進來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.84,0:19:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 有從這裡出去的方法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.95,0:20:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請帶我們逃離這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.77,0:20:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有好幾人也被抓來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.54,0:20:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯 救出請求
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈? 我說你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.57,0:20:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣把要做的事做了再說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.91,0:20:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先帶我們去你們被抓的房間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.24,0:20:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.68,0:20:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離這裡近嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.26,0:20:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.77,0:20:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫蕾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航天要塞史特拉托斯出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.14,0:20:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將於明早發動攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.72,0:20:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩幾個小時 要我們怎麼逃離啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡可是天上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.22,0:20:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說若我們逃不出去 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.73,0:20:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得和這索厄拉共存亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.79,0:20:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合國的軍隊差不多該往這邊來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.32,0:20:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會派航天要塞出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.59,0:20:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這毋庸置疑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.49,0:21:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這邊也將馬上做好出擊的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.87,0:21:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時刻終於要到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的夢想 成為現實的時候要到來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉也會高興的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 蕾拉也會的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.90,0:21:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要用這個下去 就到大家那裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.51,0:21:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 還要下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.81,0:21:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.38,0:21:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們趁現在快跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.64,0:21:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.59,0:21:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們留在這裡 只會拖他後腿的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.57,0:21:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.49,0:21:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.99,0:21:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.22,0:21:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.36,0:21:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿卡莉?

Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.65,0:23:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航天要塞內
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.95,0:23:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得知的可怕事實
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.65,0:23:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.51,0:23:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我困惑至極
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯與阿卡莉 是否平安?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.40,0:23:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周 第十一集 「假公主」

